items.badge_description: Thanks for enjoying a beer at Malmö Brewing Co. We have proudly pioneering the craft beer community with great food and beer since 2010 in Malmö, Sweden. Keep checking in beers to level up. You earn a Malmö Brewing glass when you reach 50 check-ins.
Your quest to quench your thirst leaves no stone unturned! That's at least 5 distinct venues!

Looking for more kick than a session beer, but want to be able to stay for a few rounds? You have to keep it in the middle. That's 55 beers with an ABV greater than 5% and less than 10%. Try 5 more for Level 12!

You may not be able to see through the haze, but that juicy, hoppy goodness goes down smooth. What started as a trend is here to stay. That's 10 different beers with the style of IPA - New England / Hazy, Pale Ale - New England / Hazy, IPA - Milkshake, or Pale Ale - Milkshake. Try 5 more for Level 3!
Normally DIY furniture and meatballs are all that come to mind, but now you can add Swedish beer to that list! That's 35 different beers from a brewery from Sweden. Try 5 more Level 8.

user.bio: Älskar musik, öl och Modo Hockey i både dur och moll.

items.badge_description: It's New Brew Thursday! Drink any beer you have never had before on three different Thursdays in a 20 day period.

There's beer in them thar hills! You're setting off on your journey through the world of beer, but be sure to take a little time to get to know each brewery as you go. That's a beer from 385 different breweries. Try 5 more for Level 78!

You may not be able to see through the haze, but that juicy, hoppy goodness goes down smooth. What started as a trend is here to stay. That's 150 different beers with the style of IPA - New England / Hazy, Pale Ale - New England / Hazy, IPA - Milkshake, or Pale Ale - Milkshake. Try 5 more for Level 31!
You're exploring this great country the best way possible, one delicious beer at a time! That's one beer while in at least 35 states or countries. Visit 5 more for Level 8!

Fresh from the tap is one of the best ways to enjoy a beer. Just try to use a glass and not drink directly from the tap, as tempting as it may be. That's 105 checkins with the serving style of Draft. Try 5 more for Level 22!
